  "strategy": [
    "Prioritize moving toward the marker as soon as marker_seen is detected.",
    "Use commit states to enforce consistent forward or rotational actions, preventing oscillations.",
    "After each forward commit or recovery, insert a scan state to ensure regular environment assessment.",
    "Escape obstacle_front with move_backward or full_rotate, then scan before resuming forward.",
    "Rotate away from side obstacles using commit states, then resume forward.",
    "When marker_close is detected, stop to safely complete the approach.",
    "If marker is lost, immediately enter scan_full to reacquire it.",
    "Never allow move_forward directly after obstacle_front; always pass through a recovery/scan state.",
    "Alternate between short forward runs and scans to maximize marker detection chances."
  ]
